Class ProximityObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • wifidirect.p2pcore.ProximityObserver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, peersim.cdsim.CDProtocol, peersim.core.Protocol

    public class ProximityObserver
extends Object
implements peersim.cdsim.CDProtocol
    An asynchronous update interface for receiving notifications about Proximity information as the Proximity is constructed.
